			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Okay, I've been reading through the various posts in regard to this spell and would like to add my own comment.  Please look at how this is listed (and keep in mind that everywhere I've ever seen this description, it has been typed exactly the same)<BR>
<BR>
Add - Regeneration to Pet &amp; AC &amp; STR <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Now... see how it says Add - Regeneration?    It's horrible grammar, but basically it says &quot;Add MINUS regeneration&quot; and does just that.  Your pet regenerates at such a slow rate, it's horrid.  However, that's where your bind wounds skill will come in handy to at least get your pet up to 50%.  Keep those bandages handy!
			</font>
	
